data.description: Welcome to this turn key bi-level home in the well-Established Neighborhood of Sherrelwood Estates in North Denver  On a Corner Lot with great Views of Downtown, the Mountains, and Sunsets! A Family Floor Plan with 5 Bedrooms, 2 Baths, and a Finished Full Basement provides plenty of space to live in comfort! The kitchen has stunning granite countertops matched with stainless steel appliances, and a sliding door that leads out to a spacious covered deck perfect for hosting summer barbecues and entertaining guests. The backyard/frontyard is fully landscaped with lush green grass and equipped with a dog run and a brand new fence all the way around providing privacy and a tranquil escape. Enjoy the outdoors with family and friends in the generously sized yard. Home features a new A/C unit and hot water heater, oversized two car garage and a huge corner lot to store all your toys and equipment.  Conveniently Located with Easy Access to I-25, Highway 36, I-76 and Downtown Denver, Just Minutes from Shopping, Dining, and Recreation in any Direction This home offers a perfect balance of style and functionality, don't miss this opportunity to make this beautiful home your own!
